# --- Note ---
# data/, img/, rdf/ and docs/ are part of the reproducible archive.

# --- This repository ---
# rdf/, img/ and docs/ are generated but ARE part of the archive:
# they are the deliverable and must be diffable. Do not ignore them.
# The SVGs are byte-stable (SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH + fixed svg.hashsalt), so a
# rebuild without a content change leaves git status clean.
